One little treasure each.

1899
00:59:47,360 --> 00:59:49,040
(Current unresolved mysteries)
Let's go meet

1900
00:59:49,040 --> 00:59:49,880
(1. Why were the treasures resurrected?)
Touch Today

1901
00:59:49,880 --> 00:59:52,060
(2. What secret is the curator hiding?)
Group.

1902
00:59:57,760 --> 00:59:58,280
Let's go.

1903
00:59:58,280 --> 00:59:59,120
Go.

1904
00:59:59,120 --> 01:00:00,640
(Auction Room. Exhibition Hall)

1905
01:00:00,640 --> 01:00:02,840
- Don't move!
- Don't move!

1906
01:00:04,540 --> 01:00:05,380
(Touch Today Group)

1907
01:00:05,500 --> 01:00:06,400
(Character Unlocked: Touch Today Group
Henchmen, Kong Pengrui & Yang Zhibo)

1908
01:00:06,400 --> 01:00:06,740
Don't move!

1909
01:00:06,740 --> 01:00:07,920
(Dramatic reenactment. Professional
props. Don't try this at home.)

1910
01:00:07,920 --> 01:00:08,960
- Don't move!
- Don't move!

1911
01:00:09,260 --> 01:00:10,980
(Fearless)

1912
01:00:11,280 --> 01:00:12,320
Who are they?

1913
01:00:12,320 --> 01:00:13,300
(Who are these two men
who suddenly appeared?)

1914
01:00:13,920 --> 01:00:15,480
Don't point that gun at my brother.

1915
01:00:15,480 --> 01:00:16,540
(I happen to know a thing
or two about martial arts)

1916
01:00:17,180 --> 01:00:18,540
(Attempts to intimidate
them with a glare.)

1917
01:00:18,560 --> 01:00:20,360
He looks a bit like Prince Youle.

1918
01:00:20,860 --> 01:00:23,180
(How I look is none of your business)
Don't move!

1919
01:00:23,320 --> 01:00:24,000
Boss!

1920
01:00:25,420 --> 01:00:28,460
(Boss?)

1921
01:00:28,460 --> 01:00:29,860
(Who are they calling?)

1922
01:00:30,660 --> 01:00:31,900
(There's someone behind them?)

1923
01:00:33,880 --> 01:00:34,720
Boss!

1924
01:00:34,820 --> 01:00:36,000
(Only Ding Tian
was standing behind them)

1925
01:00:36,000 --> 01:00:36,840
Boss!

1926
01:00:37,280 --> 01:00:38,400
Don't move!

1927
01:00:38,400 --> 01:00:39,980
(The "boss" they're calling
is Ding Tian?)

1928
01:00:40,680 --> 01:00:42,560
Especially you...

1929
01:00:45,120 --> 01:00:46,440
the three treasures.

1930
01:00:47,160 --> 01:00:47,680
How does he...

1931
01:00:47,680 --> 01:00:48,660
(What is Ding Tian's identity?
Why do the other two call him "Boss"?)

1932
01:00:49,800 --> 01:00:52,520
Do you know Touch Today Group?

1933
01:00:53,800 --> 01:00:54,600
I am

1934
01:00:54,600 --> 01:00:55,520
the boss.

1935
01:00:56,200 --> 01:00:57,640
Touch Today Group.

1936
01:00:58,860 --> 01:01:00,380
(The fish has taken the bait)

1937
01:01:00,720 --> 01:01:01,640
Congratulations, everyone.

1938
01:01:01,640 --> 01:01:03,400
You've secured our final auction item.

1939
01:01:04,140 --> 01:01:05,580
(The treasures have been obtained)

1940
01:01:05,840 --> 01:01:07,640
Did you find the treasures?

1941
01:01:07,700 --> 01:01:10,020
(The treasures are mine now)

1942
01:01:10,540 --> 01:01:12,540
(Ding Tian is the leader
of Touch Today Group)

1943
01:01:14,840 --> 01:01:16,760
You're the boss?

1944
01:01:17,160 --> 01:01:18,420
Boss, I...

1945
01:01:18,420 --> 01:01:19,280
(Seeking protection)
Don't move.

1946
01:01:19,980 --> 01:01:21,120
(I'll take my leave)

1947
01:01:21,120 --> 01:01:23,360
Aside from the three treasures,

1948
01:01:23,880 --> 01:01:25,000
you two...

1949
01:01:27,520 --> 01:01:29,560
Boss, you're not exactly very brave.

1950
01:01:29,560 --> 01:01:30,000
Alright.

1951
01:01:30,000 --> 01:01:30,520
Look over there.

1952
01:01:31,100 --> 01:01:32,540
(Boss, boss... not much courage)

1953
01:01:32,820 --> 01:01:34,660
(Our boss may be timid,
but he loves getting involved)

1954
01:01:34,680 --> 01:01:36,680
Aside from the three treasures,

1955
01:01:36,680 --> 01:01:38,800
the two of you discovered me today

1956
01:01:39,280 --> 01:01:40,680
and saw my true face.

1957
01:01:40,680 --> 01:01:42,920
That means you'll be coming
with me as well.

1958
01:01:42,920 --> 01:01:43,880
Do you understand?

1959
01:01:49,200 --> 01:01:49,840
Move.

1960
01:01:49,840 --> 01:01:50,680
Boss,

1961
01:01:50,680 --> 01:01:51,960
the vehicle is ready.

1962
01:01:51,960 --> 01:01:53,080
We can leave at any time.

1963
01:01:53,080 --> 01:01:55,080
Boss, should we change your clothes?

1964
01:01:55,080 --> 01:01:56,640
That outfit is far too conspicuous.

1965
01:01:58,600 --> 01:01:59,800
What do you know?

1966
01:01:59,800 --> 01:02:02,000
This is what handsome looks like.

1967
01:02:04,720 --> 01:02:05,480
How adorable.

1968
01:02:05,480 --> 01:02:06,540
(This boss is unexpectedly cute)

1969
01:02:07,920 --> 01:02:08,640
No, Boss...

1970
01:02:08,640 --> 01:02:09,080
I should...

1971
01:02:09,080 --> 01:02:10,120
Quiet.

1972
01:02:10,120 --> 01:02:10,840
Yes, Boss.

1973
01:02:10,840 --> 01:02:12,520
Stop talking. Why are you even speaking?

1974
01:02:12,520 --> 01:02:14,080
Alright.

1975
01:02:14,080 --> 01:02:15,280
Yes, Boss.

1976
01:02:20,220 --> 01:02:25,020
(What is The Touch
Today Group really plotting?)

1977
01:02:28,160 --> 01:02:30,300
Why have we changed into these clothes?

1978
01:02:30,300 --> 01:02:30,900
(The ancient figures
are struggling to adjust)

1979
01:02:37,960 --> 01:02:39,440
Where is he taking us?

1980
01:02:39,440 --> 01:02:40,120
What clothing is this?

1981
01:02:40,340 --> 01:02:41,320
(It's my first time wearing something
like this. I'm a little nervous)

1982
01:02:41,320 --> 01:02:42,680
Stop fooling around.

1983
01:02:42,680 --> 01:02:43,440
Behave yourselves.

1984
01:02:43,500 --> 01:02:45,580
(Don't forget that you've
been kidnapped)

1985
01:02:45,600 --> 01:02:46,640
Hey, let's move out.

1986
01:02:47,680 --> 01:02:48,440
Where are we going?

1987
01:02:48,440 --> 01:02:49,120
Where?

1988
01:02:49,620 --> 01:02:51,220
(Where are they being taken?)

1989
01:02:51,520 --> 01:02:53,280
Buddy, follow the car in front.

1990
01:02:53,720 --> 01:02:54,600
Follow the car.

1991
01:03:01,640 --> 01:03:02,480
What's with you?

1992
01:03:02,480 --> 01:03:03,480
You're awfully full of yourself.

1993
01:03:03,480 --> 01:03:04,760
Who exactly are you?

1994
01:03:04,760 --> 01:03:05,960
I'm one of the good guys.

1995
01:03:05,960 --> 01:03:07,080
If you're one of the good guys,

1996
01:03:07,080 --> 01:03:08,080
why are you tying us up?

1997
01:03:08,720 --> 01:03:09,800
You'll understand

1998
01:03:09,800 --> 01:03:11,600
my good intentions soon enough, alright?

1999
01:03:12,920 --> 01:03:13,360
What?

2000
01:03:13,360 --> 01:03:14,320
What are you trying to do today?

2001
01:03:14,320 --> 01:03:15,680
Why are you taking us with you?

2002
01:03:15,680 --> 01:03:16,960
Stop asking so many questions.

2003
01:03:16,960 --> 01:03:18,880
There aren't that many whys.

2004
01:03:19,160 --> 01:03:20,920
Just follow me, alright?

2005
01:03:22,480 --> 01:03:23,720
I'll let you keep acting so tough.

2006
01:03:24,880 --> 01:03:26,440
This is highly suspicious.

2007
01:03:26,440 --> 01:03:26,880
It really is.

2008
01:03:27,360 --> 01:03:28,200
Something feels very off.

2009
01:03:28,200 --> 01:03:29,880
Kidnapping the three
treasures is one thing,

2010
01:03:29,880 --> 01:03:30,920
but why am I involved?

2011
01:03:30,940 --> 01:03:32,980
(What is Touch Today Group
true purpose in abducting them?)

2012
01:03:33,060 --> 01:03:35,580
One righteous cause.

2013
01:03:36,300 --> 01:03:38,860
One righteous cause
saves the common folk.

2014
01:03:38,900 --> 01:03:40,860
(What kind of passphrase is this?)

2015
01:03:40,880 --> 01:03:42,280
One righteous cause

2016
01:03:42,280 --> 01:03:43,640
saves the common folk.

2017
01:03:43,640 --> 01:03:46,780
(How did Jin Da know the countersign?)

2018
01:03:46,800 --> 01:03:47,160
We're allies.

2019
01:03:48,120 --> 01:03:48,480
We're allies.

2020
01:03:50,360 --> 01:03:51,120
Pull over.

2021
01:03:53,840 --> 01:03:55,720
I'm an undercover agent
inside Touch Today Group.

2022
01:03:55,720 --> 01:03:57,240
(An undercover operative
within Touch Today Group)

2023
01:03:57,240 --> 01:03:59,400
Do you know where we're supposed to go?

2024
01:04:00,000 --> 01:04:00,560
I do.

2025
01:04:00,560 --> 01:04:01,400
I have a location.

2026
01:04:02,280 --> 01:04:03,720
(Jin Da knows the destination)
Someone sent me the coordinates.

2027
01:04:03,720 --> 01:04:04,840
(Collaborator: A helpful contact)
They said we could meet them there.

2028
01:04:04,840 --> 01:04:06,000
(A mysterious location)

2029
01:04:06,000 --> 01:04:07,480
Alright, let's navigate there.

2030
01:04:07,480 --> 01:04:08,480
Where are we going?

2031
01:04:09,540 --> 01:04:10,320
(She seems highly suspicious)

2032
01:04:10,320 --> 01:04:12,120
Be careful.

2033
01:04:12,120 --> 01:04:13,160
Don't give yourself away.

2034
01:04:13,160 --> 01:04:14,740
(She's drawn the detectives' suspicion)
Don't blow your cover.

2035
01:04:15,680 --> 01:04:16,920
Where are we going?

2036
01:04:16,980 --> 01:04:18,460
(Who sent Jin Da the coordinates,
and why are they going there?)

2037
01:04:19,480 --> 01:04:21,000
(The lead vehicle changes direction.
Where is it headed?)

2038
01:04:21,000 --> 01:04:22,080
This route doesn't seem right either.

2039
01:04:22,240 --> 01:04:23,040
What should we do?

2040
01:04:23,040 --> 01:04:23,680
Follow them.

2041
01:04:23,680 --> 01:04:24,360
Let's stay on them.

2042
01:04:28,360 --> 01:04:30,800
This route is definitely wrong.

2043
01:04:31,520 --> 01:04:32,960
If you think the route is wrong,
ask the driver.

2044
01:04:32,960 --> 01:04:34,880
Who else are you asking? Ask yourself.

2045
01:04:34,880 --> 01:04:36,240
This route isn't right.

2046
01:04:36,240 --> 01:04:37,120
I'm not the one driving.

2047
01:04:37,120 --> 01:04:38,440
Why don't you ask the driver?

2048
01:04:38,440 --> 01:04:39,990
(Watch how you speak to the boss)
Driver, what's going on?

2049
01:04:40,000 --> 01:04:40,520
Give it to him.

2050
01:04:40,520 --> 01:04:41,640
Take off your sock.

2051
01:04:41,640 --> 01:04:42,520
Stuff it in his mouth.

2052
01:04:42,520 --> 01:04:42,720
Go on.

2053
01:04:42,720 --> 01:04:43,220
Stuff it in.

2054
01:04:43,220 --> 01:04:44,060
(Instantly silenced)

2055
01:04:46,680 --> 01:04:47,440
Look at that symbol.

2056
01:04:47,800 --> 01:04:48,200
R.

2057
01:04:49,560 --> 01:04:50,600
R. See it?

2058
01:04:51,160 --> 01:04:51,920
Where?

2059
01:04:51,920 --> 01:04:53,240
On the wall.

2060
01:04:53,700 --> 01:04:55,000
(The "R" symbol on the wall.)

2061
01:04:55,000 --> 01:04:56,080
There's an R marked on the wall.

2062
01:04:57,680 --> 01:04:59,120
Where? I don't see any R.

2063
01:04:59,120 --> 01:04:59,800
You...

2064
01:05:00,280 --> 01:05:01,080
I don't see any R.

2065
01:05:01,080 --> 01:05:02,320
Right there on the gray wall.

2066
01:05:04,580 --> 01:05:05,660
(The sunglasses are affecting
his vision)

2067
01:05:05,680 --> 01:05:07,640
This must be the infamous

2068
01:05:07,640 --> 01:05:08,360
R Corporation.

2069
01:05:08,360 --> 01:05:09,120
Boss,

2070
01:05:09,720 --> 01:05:10,840
where have you brought us?

2071
01:05:11,120 --> 01:05:13,280
To the territory
of a criminal organization,

2072
01:05:13,280 --> 01:05:15,040
one that's opposed to me.

2073
01:05:15,300 --> 01:05:17,140
(What exactly is R Corporation?)

2074
01:05:17,180 --> 01:05:18,140
(Unlock the detective team's
best moments early)

2075
01:05:18,140 --> 01:05:19,040
(At every Tuesday noon,
Dungeon Unlocking)

2076
01:05:19,040 --> 01:05:21,120
Is this R Corporation's territory?

2077
01:05:21,120 --> 01:05:22,880
Why have we come to R Corporation?

2078
01:05:22,880 --> 01:05:23,520
You're asking me?

2079
01:05:24,440 --> 01:05:25,680
(Who else would know?)
You kidnapped us and brought us here.

2080
01:05:26,360 --> 01:05:28,240
What? You're questioning me now?

2081
01:05:29,480 --> 01:05:30,480
Who gives you the right?

2082
01:05:30,480 --> 01:05:31,880
You've got a gun in your hand.

2083
01:05:31,880 --> 01:05:32,080
Go on.

2084
01:05:32,560 --> 01:05:33,360
Fire a shot.

2085
01:05:33,360 --> 01:05:34,320
Go on. Fire.

2086
01:05:34,320 --> 01:05:35,100
(Dramatic reenactment. Professional
props. Don't try this at home.)

2087
01:05:35,180 --> 01:05:36,400
(Enjoy your arrogance while it lasts)

2088
01:05:36,400 --> 01:05:37,200
Behave yourself.

2089
01:05:37,200 --> 01:05:37,640
Understood?

2090
01:05:38,320 --> 01:05:39,680
In a moment, keep pretending

2091
01:05:39,680 --> 01:05:41,040
to threaten us as before.

2092
01:05:41,040 --> 01:05:42,200
Stay undercover.

2093
01:05:42,200 --> 01:05:43,600
We'll coordinate from both
inside and outside.

2094
01:05:43,600 --> 01:05:44,900
(Henchman continues
his undercover mission)

2095
01:05:46,480 --> 01:05:47,320
Why did they get out?

2096
01:05:47,320 --> 01:05:48,000
Who got out?

2097
01:05:51,840 --> 01:05:53,080
Why did my subordinate get out as well?

2098
01:05:55,000 --> 01:05:56,080
He forced them out.

2099
01:05:56,760 --> 01:05:57,480
Stay where you are.

2100
01:05:57,480 --> 01:05:59,000
(Dramatic reenactment. Professional
props. Don't try this at home.)

2101
01:05:59,000 --> 01:06:00,080
What happens if this goes off?

2102
01:06:00,080 --> 01:06:00,680
You'll die.

2103
01:06:00,680 --> 01:06:01,480
(Don't scare me)

2104
01:06:01,480 --> 01:06:02,680
You're from the past. You wouldn't know.

2105
01:06:03,360 --> 01:06:03,760
Get out.

2106
01:06:04,600 --> 01:06:05,600
Move it.

2107
01:06:05,600 --> 01:06:06,160
Now.

2108
01:06:06,720 --> 01:06:07,360
Raise your hands.

2109
01:06:18,960 --> 01:06:19,840
What's going on?

2110
01:06:19,840 --> 01:06:20,960
Where is this?

2111
01:06:22,560 --> 01:06:23,840
There's an R symbol over there,
isn't there?

2112
01:06:26,520 --> 01:06:27,160
Yes.

2113
01:06:28,280 --> 01:06:29,680
Let's check his arm.

2114
01:06:29,680 --> 01:06:30,520
R.

2115
01:06:31,340 --> 01:06:32,820
(This place is connected
to the curator?)

2116
01:06:33,680 --> 01:06:35,680
Something isn't right about this place.

2117
01:06:35,680 --> 01:06:36,880
How did we end up here?

2118
01:06:36,880 --> 01:06:38,240
(This was not Touch
Today Group's original destination)

2119
01:06:38,240 --> 01:06:39,840
Why have we come here?

2120
01:06:39,840 --> 01:06:40,440
Exactly.

2121
01:06:40,440 --> 01:06:42,440
We followed the car in front.

2122
01:06:42,440 --> 01:06:43,640
How did we end up here?

2123
01:06:45,840 --> 01:06:46,800
Why did it bring us here?

2124
01:06:47,320 --> 01:06:47,880
Traitor.

2125
01:06:51,680 --> 01:06:52,560
Alright.

2126
01:06:52,560 --> 01:06:53,200
I'll tell you.

2127
01:06:53,200 --> 01:06:55,720
It was actually me
who brought everyone here.

2128
01:06:55,820 --> 01:06:58,620
(Why did Jin Da bring everyone here?)

2129
01:06:58,960 --> 01:06:59,560
What do you mean?

2130
01:07:00,400 --> 01:07:01,920
Who exactly are you?

2131
01:07:01,940 --> 01:07:04,380
(What is Jin Da's true identity?)

2132
01:07:04,400 --> 01:07:05,840
Alright.

2133
01:07:06,280 --> 01:07:07,640
It's my turn now.

2134
01:07:08,720 --> 01:07:10,080
This is your place?

2135
01:07:10,530 --> 01:07:12,240
I joined an organization.

2136
01:07:12,300 --> 01:07:14,580
(Jin Da joined
a mysterious organization)

2137
01:07:14,600 --> 01:07:16,800
Within that organization,
there is a helpful contact

2138
01:07:16,800 --> 01:07:18,500
(Collaborator: The Helpful Contact)
who has been communicating with me.

2139
01:07:18,560 --> 01:07:20,520
To be honest, I don't know much myself.

2140
01:07:20,520 --> 01:07:21,840
All they told me today

2141
01:07:21,840 --> 01:07:24,240
was to bring the treasures
here after obtaining them.

2142
01:07:24,780 --> 01:07:27,300
(Why was Jin Da told
to bring the three treasures here?)

2143
01:07:27,300 --> 01:07:27,940
(Voice Call)

2144
01:07:27,980 --> 01:07:29,380
(Collaborator: Helpful Contact)

2145
01:07:31,000 --> 01:07:32,000
I've arrived.

2146
01:07:32,520 --> 01:07:33,320
I'll be there shortly.

2147
01:07:33,320 --> 01:07:33,720
Alright.

2148
01:07:33,720 --> 01:07:34,160
Wait for me.

2149
01:07:34,160 --> 01:07:35,000
We'll wait.

2150
01:07:35,360 --> 01:07:35,720
Who is it?

2151
01:07:38,720 --> 01:07:39,520
Everyone.

2152
01:07:39,520 --> 01:07:40,440
Hold on.

2153
01:07:43,840 --> 01:07:44,640
Thank you

2154
01:07:44,640 --> 01:07:47,960
for bringing the three treasures here.

2155
01:07:47,960 --> 01:07:49,040
Mission accomplished.

2156
01:07:51,200 --> 01:07:52,560
Who are you?

2157
01:07:52,560 --> 01:07:54,360
Take one more step, and I'll shoot her.

2158
01:08:01,960 --> 01:08:03,720
It seems none of you
understand the situation.

2159
01:08:08,600 --> 01:08:10,560
Apparently, none of you
understand it at all.

2160
01:08:13,880 --> 01:08:15,080
Guys!

2161
01:08:15,680 --> 01:08:16,560
What is he doing?

2162
01:08:18,880 --> 01:08:19,600
So many of them.

2163
01:08:22,240 --> 01:08:22,800
What's going on?

2164
01:08:25,220 --> 01:08:26,420
(This way, please)
What are you trying to do?

2165
01:08:28,470 --> 01:08:29,350
Guys!

2166
01:08:29,350 --> 01:08:31,430
Take these six people
over there and lock them up.

2167
01:08:31,620 --> 01:08:32,430
(Lock them up?)

2168
01:08:32,430 --> 01:08:32,920
Wait.

2169
01:08:34,000 --> 01:08:34,600
Lock us up?

2170
01:08:34,600 --> 01:08:36,080
Aren't you on the same side?

2171
01:08:36,080 --> 01:08:36,800
No.

